snippet.textDisplay:
Please explain to us the case of Renata Voracova. 
Her situation, which has just been detained, further exposes how Djokovic is being used as a scapegoat for the sole purpose of a federal election and political gain. 

This Czech unkown female player had her exemption considered VALID during her passage to the customs and was able to reside SEVERAL DAYS in the country to play a tournament without being worried in the least before the arrival of Novak. 

Australian  authorities removed her only AFTER that some sources close to Tennis Australia revealed that at least three other participants in the Australian Open with the same medical exemption as Novak Djokovic were already in the country. 
It's only after those revelations, australian authorities decided to act... that's just a suspicious and shameful timing. 🤦‍♂️ 

Please explain to us how she got through customs and why her exemption is no longer considered valid only after the Djokovic case? Why the authorities waited several days after her arrival to apprehend her and only after Djokovic’s call 

If Djokovic had forfeited, I am sure that Renata Voracova would not have seen her exemption cancelled and that she would participate at the Australian Open 

Huge hypocrisy from the Australian prime minister Morrison who obviously will close his mouth about this story, too focus on Djokovic to increase his popularity.

Starting from the point where he and his team believed he was compliant - OK. Case given athletes need to train or will come up short - to fast track, not as special treatment but good PR and Australian authorities being smart for their own public perception.

I guess it comes down to of the very high numbers of people who move over borders with a pandemic and a mutating virus - let’s not slag off authorities to pander to the majority of those unvaccinated who enjoy being difficult rather than following the science - making up their own. The vaccines are not rushed, containing smoothies of unborn babies, pork or micro chips put there by Bill Gates.

Many football supporters hearts beat a lot faster during games. No reports of supporters taken ill in after the first half ends at any match. 

Either we want to mitigate the effects of the pandemic and work together or we want to be difficult and let it spread. 

If NJ has a case it really should have been fast tracked - costs a fortune having police outside hotel. Disruptive to others in the hotel.

He thinks he can pull strings here in Australia like he does in Serbia, and by the way, his place of residence is Monaco!!  What a great patriot he is, to avoid paying Serbian income tax on his winnings and sponsarships.    Yet the Serbian government are making a song and dance about him.   Makes you wonder why????   Djokovic and his hangers-on are full of bullshit and have been found out.   Us Australians have gone through the veritable wringer over the last 2 years with COVID.   In Victoria, we have had 6 lockdowns and had massive restrictions on movements outside of lockdown.  We have also been restricted from leaving the country as well.   This tool walzes into the country, espousing his anti-vaccination position and then expects to be welcome with open arms.   Mate, we are furious with that numbnut’s behaviour and would gladly see him and anyone else who chooses this path turfed out of the country immediately.    Grüße aus Australien.
